Event Sentence: Other cabinet ministers have done their bit while NSA, Ajit Doval, flies under the radar but is working on security relationships across the region.This week it was the turn of minister of state MJ Akbar to engage the Iranian leadership, after visiting Iraq, Syria and Lebanon, while VK Singh has been helming government’s diaspora outreach and mass evacuations from the region’s troubled spots.In the coming months, India will play host to leaders from UAE, Saudi Arabia and Qatar and Iran from the Gulf region, while president of Israel, Reuven Rivlin is expected to return Mukherjee’s visit.
Headline: After acting East, India is now thinking West
